<p>
  The topic bar appears below the tab bar and shows the current channel name, active modes, and topic text.
</p>
<p>
  For PMs, it shows "Private conversation with &lt;nickname&gt;". For the Status tab, it shows "RetroHexChat Status".
</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_link}>See Also</.help_h4>
<p><.help_link topic="cmd-topic">/topic Command</.help_link></p>
